{"sn36.22:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 36.22 ","sn36.22:0.2":"3. Atthasatapariyayavagga ","sn36.22:0.3":"Atthasatasutta ","sn36.22:1.1":"“Atthasatapariyayam vo, bhikkhave, dhammapariyayam desessami. ","sn36.22:1.2":"Tam sunatha. ","sn36.22:1.3":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, atthasatapariyayo, dhammapariyayo? ","sn36.22:1.4":"Dvepi maya, bhikkhave, vedana vutta pariyayena; ","sn36.22:1.5":"tissopi maya vedana vutta pariyayena; ","sn36.22:1.6":"pancapi maya vedana vutta pariyayena; ","sn36.22:1.7":"chapi maya vedana vutta pariyayena; ","sn36.22:1.8":"attharasapi maya vedana vutta pariyayena; ","sn36.22:1.9":"chattimsapi maya vedana vutta pariyayena; ","sn36.22:1.10":"atthasatampi maya vedana vutta pariyayena. ","sn36.22:2.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, dve vedana? ","sn36.22:2.2":"Kayika ca cetasika ca—","sn36.22:2.3":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, dve vedana. ","sn36.22:2.4":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, tisso vedana? ","sn36.22:2.5":"Sukha vedana, dukkha vedana, adukkhamasukha vedana—","sn36.22:2.6":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, tisso vedana. ","sn36.22:2.7":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, panca vedana? ","sn36.22:2.8":"Sukhindriyam, dukkhindriyam, somanassindriyam, domanassindriyam, upekkhindriyam—","sn36.22:2.9":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, panca vedana. ","sn36.22:2.10":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, cha vedana? ","sn36.22:2.11":"Cakkhusamphassaja vedana …pe… ","sn36.22:2.12":"manosamphassaja vedana—","sn36.22:2.13":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, cha vedana. ","sn36.22:2.14":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, attharasa vedana? ","sn36.22:2.15":"Cha somanassupavicara, cha domanassupavicara, cha upekkhupavicara—","sn36.22:2.16":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, attharasa vedana. ","sn36.22:2.17":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, chattimsa vedana? ","sn36.22:2.18":"Cha gehasitani somanassani, cha nekkhammasitani somanassani, cha gehasitani domanassani, cha nekkhammasitani domanassani, cha gehasita upekkha, cha nekkhammasita upekkha—","sn36.22:2.19":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, chattimsa vedana. ","sn36.22:2.20":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, atthasatam vedana? ","sn36.22:2.21":"Atita chattimsa vedana, anagata chattimsa vedana, paccuppanna chattimsa vedana—","sn36.22:2.22":"ima vuccanti, bhikkhave, atthasatam vedana. ","sn36.22:2.23":"Ayam, bhikkhave, atthasatapariyayo dhammapariyayo”ti. ","sn36.22:2.24":"Dutiyam. "}